  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示FinTech_LedgerService如何调用认证和支付服务。核心场景是：API客户端发起请求，经过设备控制器，最终落到交易队列处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到了LedgerService，但后面又说AuthVault。这两个都是FinTech_前缀的服务，我需要确认：DeviceController对应的是AuthVault还是独立的服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "DeviceController就是FinTech_AuthVault，它负责鉴权和设备管理。APIClient是FinTech_LedgerService，作为入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我先画第一条线：FinTech_LedgerService发送过滤条件给FinTech_AuthVault。这里有个细节——过滤条件的载体需要单独表示吗？比如一个叫DeviceFilterInput的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，DeviceFilterInput代表实际的过滤参数，但它本身也是一个服务——FinTech_PaymentGateway，负责解析和校验支付相关的过滤条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在AuthVault会使用PaymentGateway来处理过滤输入。接下来AuthVault需要把实际的数据获取委托出去，这里应该是FinTech_TransactionQueue对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TransactionQueue是核心，它负责异步拉取交易数据。不过它还需要一个数据源，我们内部叫FinTech_AuthVault——等等，这和前面的AuthVault重名了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "检测到命名冲突。您刚才说TransactionQueue的数据源也是FinTech_AuthVault，但DeviceController已经是AuthVault了。这是同一个服务被复用，还是数据源应该是另一个服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，数据源确实是FinTech_AuthVault——这是设计上的循环依赖，AuthVault既作为控制器入口，也作为底层数据存储。保持命名一致，让TransactionQueue指向同一个AuthVault节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。现在流程是：TransactionQueue应用过滤条件到AuthVault数据源，获取结果后返回给AuthVault控制器。最后需要画回到LedgerService的响应线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，形成闭环。DeviceDataFetcher把结果返回给DeviceController，然后DeviceController再响应APIClient。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下边的标注：LedgerService到AuthVault是\"sends filter input\"，AuthVault到PaymentGateway是\"uses\"，AuthVault到TransactionQueue是\"delegates\"，TransactionQueue到AuthVault是\"applies filters\"，返回的两条边分别是\"returns results\"和\"responds\"。这样准确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "准确。这个流程体现了分层设计：LedgerService作为API层，AuthVault作为控制层协调PaymentGateway和TransactionQueue，最终数据仍落回AuthVault存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程图已完成。六个节点、六条边，覆盖了FinTech_LedgerService经AuthVault协调PaymentGateway与TransactionQueue完成数据查询的完整链路。",
